lead_paragraph: Chris Young struck out 10 in six innings, Mike Moustakas homered, doubled twice and drove in three runs, and the Kansas City Royals beat the Baltimore Orioles 4-2 Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Young Has 10 Ks, Moustakas Hits HR as Royals Beat Orioles
